wdi2-SH.MED.NUMW.P3.def: Nurses and midwives include professional nurses, professional midwives, auxiliary nurses, auxiliary midwives, enrolled nurses, enrolled midwives and other associated personnel, such as dental nurses and primary care nurses.
wdi2-SH.MED.NUMW.P3.name: Nurses and midwives
wdi2-SH.MED.NUMW.P3.source: World Health Organization's Global Health Workforce Statistics, OECD, supplemented by country data.
